{"product_id": "12120", "page": 10, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2018-02-04", "text": "This is the real OG\nBest story and gameplay of any of the GTA games. This is the one that made them blow up to fame.\nEven though it hasn't been remastered or upgraded to HD it's still very playable. Has selection for 1920x1080p and you can tweak the controls from auto aim to free aim. The music brought back so many memories...\nWorth the buy.\nI'll update this review if I find any bugs or controller issues.", "hours": 8.0, "user_id": "76561198307615811", "username": "TaggersZ", "products": 578, "early_access": false}
