{"product_id": "12120", "page": 57, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-28", "text": "I've got 100% completion in this game 5 times so far (I used to play it pre-Steam, my playtime here isn't correct, it's over 300 hours) and I still get the same satisfaction and excitement every time I start the game. It represents such an important part of my gaming history.\nThe soundtrack is great, the story is one of the best in GTA history (I like GTA IV more), the customisation of CJ, the side storylines, the city... I love everything about it, I know every part of Los Santos by heart.\nI recommend it for everyone, literally.", "hours": 13.4, "username": "F.", "products": 294, "early_access": false}
