{"product_id": "12120", "page": 78, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-11-23", "text": "Easily my favourite Grand Theft Auto game; If not for the nostalgia, for the deep yet quirky story that will have you replaying it for years to come.\nRight now I'm doing my 7th playthrough of the game (1st on PC), going for my 2nd 100% completion. Thoroughly enjoying it and I'm even picking up little things I hadn't noticed on previous runs to this day. Couldn't reccomend this higher if you are a fan of the newer games and want to go back to the series roots (very good place to start) or to people who have never really sat down infront of a GTA game for longer than 6 hours before and want to know what the hype is all about.", "hours": 85.1, "username": "JobroCodwawz", "products": 84, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
