{"product_id": "12120", "page": 100, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-13", "text": "Typically, this is not the kind of game I'd choose to play. But for nostalgia sake (saw my cousin playing it decades ago) and a bit curiosity, I decided to buy and try it for myself.\nBest purchase ever.\nFun missions, hours and hours of compelling gameplay & story, I barely realized I played this games for 12 hours straight in my weekend! The characters are also really colorful and memorable; the crazy hyperbolic world of gangsters and criminal underworld is new for me yet it was so refreshing.\nI've recently finished this game, and I still have some side missions and things to do for 100% completion. Will take my sweet time to do it while leisurely wandering around the cities.\nGrove 4 Life!", "hours": 110.4, "username": "kuroha.ai", "products": 7, "early_access": false}
