{"product_id": "12120", "page": 101, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-11", "text": "An amazing feat for the time, and a game-changing accomplishment for consoles and the PC alike. There's no end to the amount of fun you can have with San Andreas. The campaign is great and very replayable, but the fun never ends with mods. There's even a mod to play the game online. Two, actually. San Andreas Multiplayer (SAMP) and Multi Theft Auto (MTA). The online community for San Andreas is so much better than GTA V's. There are many online gamemodes like racing, deathmatch, and roleplay. The community is mature and kind to new players. The game as a whole is great, and I definitely recommend to any open world fan.", "hours": 169.8, "user_id": "76561198190459998", "username": "ivybones", "products": 65, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
