{"product_id": "12120", "page": 119, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-09-01", "text": "TL;DR: This is a terrible port pushed out by Rockstar for Steam to grab some cash.\nWhen I fired up this Steam version I had a feeling that my memories of enjoying this game must have been faulty, because it is U-G-L-Y. It turns out that the Steam version is its own particular version, which is a severe downgrade from the original PC release, which has several updates this version didn't get. The differences have been outlined by several people, like in this one:\n.\nThe game can apparently be modded so it isn't such a bad port, but there are so many other games worth playing, even within this series, so \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 it.", "hours": 37.5, "username": "Cthulhu Calamari /|\\(;,;)/|\\", "products": 422, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 119, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-09-01", "text": "One of the best GTA games ever made along with VC! I've played this game since 2006, so when I was a very little kid and I still play it even today. I completed the main storyline about 4 times.\nThe storyline is simply amazing, it keeps you going, it's very easy to mod (you'll need to downgrade your game to v1 version), unlimited character customization, unlimited freeroam, alot of fun mini-games, tons of fun cheat codes, unofficial multiplayer mods (SA-MP/MTA) with many gamemodes which are still popular even today!\nThe graphics may of course be dated, but keep in mind, this is a 2004 game and graphics don't really matter when you have everything else.\nHowever there are few bugs in this game if you play it on modern PCs, most of them can be fixed by turning on Frame Limiter and installing Silent's patch, I'd also recommend Widescreen patches if you want to play true widescreen.\nOtherwise this game is just pure art. There are even more things than I've mentioned, but that's the main things I wanted to say! You won't regret playing this game at all.\nThank you for one of my most childhood memories, Rockstar.", "hours": 47.5, "username": "UnKn0wN \u208d\u208d (\u0e07 \u02d8\u03c9\u02d8 )\u0e27 \u207e\u207e", "products": 185, "early_access": false}
