{"product_id": "12120", "page": 261, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-01-24", "text": "Picked this up when i was 4 on release, Tried to play it with my ps1 controller but my ps2 was like nah get the ps2 controller you\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 spent hours on this game and become a proper gangster, I would shoot people all day everyday, it got say back i even did drive-bys in school.\nI had to pick this game up on PC just to see the graphics ya know, well it is a beautiful game to mod on. I turned CJ into the hulk and smashed the \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ing city, i was even able to smack that dirty \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 who sucked me off in the car and ran off with my money, the \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 was\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665too tbh.\nBut \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 it anyways, good game.", "hours": 4.9, "username": "Brents", "products": 303, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
