{"product_id": "12120", "page": 379, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-10-11", "text": "You might just find your new favorite game of all time when you play this game. By far the greatest of the GTA franchise, This game puts you in the shoes of Carl CJ Johnson(i own this game on PS2/PS3/PC). In this game you must defend your gang from others by destroying supply shipments, killing other gang members and all around chaos for your enemies gangs.\n(PS this is my 3rd out of 4 copies of San Andreas that i own)\nPC port:8/10\nother versions:9.5/10\nMobile port:7/10", "hours": 5.5, "username": "thesevenneedles", "products": 104, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 379, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-10-11", "text": "Got this game\nFirst GTA game I have ever played\nHated the controls with a passion.\nCouldn't get used to driving. Failed OG loc mission 5 million times.\nAsked steam for refund\nDidn't get it\nDecided to play it some more because i might as well.\nFound i could turn off \"mouse controls steering\"\nTurned off \"mouse controls steering\"\nLoved the game\nLoved the controls\nLoved everything\nI followed the damn train\nPeople can say I didn't know why I followed the train\nBut they can never say i didn't follow it.\nAnd even though they removed songs, its still a good game.\nJust because it isn't as good as it once was, doesn't mean it isn't a good game.", "hours": 54.4, "username": "Dr.Joto", "products": 221, "early_access": false}
