{"product_id": "12120", "page": 469, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-04-09", "text": "Another sorry\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665port by Rockstar.\nIt's missing 17 songs, game either runs at 25 FPS, or wonky physics at 60+ FPS, has no option for 1080p, button prompts are still listed as keybindings even when you enable the joypad, it is not moddable, has no SA MP, I could go on.\nYou're better off pirating this game.\nI only play it because i've downgraded it to the right version, but it's not really worth the trouble. And i'm only recommending it because the game itself is still there, just with a\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665ton of tiny \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665 ups and goofs.\nNostalgia aside, this is one of the best games of all time. Lots of map variety, lot of missions, lot of RPG stats, the characters are interesting and diverse, you know the deal.", "hours": 52.9, "username": "Gilbertify", "products": 140, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
