{"product_id": "12120", "page": 476, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-03-18", "text": "Without a doubt the best GTA-game to date. The large island of San Andreas is huge and contains three very large and detailed cities. The nature of world is also very varied, with mountains in the west, desert in the north and hilly grassland in the south.\nBetween the three large cities of Las Venturas, Los Santos and San Fierro you have a pretty large amount of small towns, lakes, railroads and much much more. Combine the huge world with a seemingly unlimited amount of side missions and activities and a very well written story and you get a extremely entertaining game.\nThis is one of my all-time favorite games and is still in my opinion Rockstars greatest title to date.", "hours": 12.6, "user_id": "76561198049992458", "username": "SERI0US", "products": 441, "early_access": false}
