{"product_id": "12120", "page": 531, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-12-08", "text": "Finished this a while ago, but today figured I'd load up the old save and wreak havoc. Problem is, when I loaded the game, it brought me to the first cutscene and the beginning of the game. I try a restart. Again, same thing. Pity, it's a good game, but this port is ruined by a sloppy system of saves being ruined by updates.\nThere's apparently a user made save editor that can convert the game's saves to newer versions an save them, but I tried it and it isn't working.\nAll I can say is Rockstar, we get it. You can't stand pc gamers after the Hot Coffee incident, but you could at least pretend to like us.", "hours": 11.8, "username": "Zuko", "products": 124, "early_access": false}
