{"product_id": "12120", "page": 555, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-10-25", "text": "The games really cool, has the gangsta atmosphere and a sense of humour making the story really enjoyable.\nAlthough people complain that some kind of editting has been done and content removed, i didn't notice any of that missing. The only annoying thing about San Andreas was the controls and behaviour of the car/npcs - maybe I was unlucky but it happened so often that it really annoyed me (especially in mid-mission when suddeny your car behaves like it was not metal and rolls and you fail).\nThe missions in the later part of the game get old-school, hardcore, you really have to be skilled not to die and finish sth on time.\nAll in all, a really good GTF title, go for it, and meet the homies :)", "hours": 75.5, "user_id": "76561198069877806", "username": "ur Game Buddy", "products": 275, "early_access": false}
