{"product_id": "12120", "page": 579, "page_order": 9, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-08-04", "text": "So yeah, this Steam version is really bad. I can't mod the damn game, so I can't play SA-MP if i wanted to because its not supported due to this stupid mandatory update. 18 songs have been removed, most of the resolution support is gone, and save files are deleted. What's funny is that they finally decided to update the game after 10 YEARS! I have an old CD copy of the game and guess what? Has everything they took away from us. I got my money back and I'm just using my old copy of the game in which is still in perfect condition. Don't buy this game on Steam, either find a copy on Ebay, or pirate the damn thing because this version is not worth it.", "hours": 0.2, "username": "Brahma", "products": 125, "found_funny": 6, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 580, "page_order": 0, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-08-03", "text": "GTA: San Andreas is an absolutely amazing game, and far better in terms of story than all other GTAs. Who cares if the graphics are godawful? A game this this big with GTA V graphics would be literally impossible to run in 2003 unless you actually borrowed NASA's computer. Anyways, here's the pros and cons of the game.\nWeapons\n+Some awesome weapons\n-Most of the weapons are ludicrously outclassed by other weapons of the same category, like the RPG compared to the Minigun\n+Several weapon categories allows you to pick your favorite weapon of, say, the SMG class (Tec-9, MAC-10, or MP-5) and use that weapon without having to cycle through other weapons like you would in GTA V\nVehicles and Driver AI\n+A huge variety of vehicles, from the beautiful and powerful Bullet (Ford GT), to the huge and slow Combine Harvester\n+You can find just about any vehicle in the game on the street, with some exceptions such as the SWAT tank or the Mothership\n-The NPC Driver AI is absolute garbage. I could probably make a better AI back in the 90s. You can't go anywhere on the highway without witnessing a crash.\n-Road rage\n+There's a Ford GT\n-There's no McLaren F1\n+NPCs never crash into you", "hours": 249.8, "username": "sky does fortnite", "products": 77, "early_access": false}
