{"product_id": "12120", "page": 586, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-07-18", "text": "Such a great game, you can get so immersed in this. There's so much to do, I haven't even played many of the missions because I'm having so much fun doing whatever I want, wherever I want and whenever I want. Grab spray paint and choke hookers to death. Jetpack on top of buildings. Modify cars. Go on police and ambulance missions. Steal from peoples houses at night. Go to a strip club. Its just so fun, the game doesn't take itself too seriously which I love. Just grab a baton and beat the\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665outa the first random innocent civilian you see, because why not? The city is very alive you've got a lot of things to interact with, clothes shops, gym, fast food, gun shop. Its just great. I would recommend to anyone.", "hours": 11.9, "username": "Holocene", "products": 171, "early_access": false}
