{"product_id": "12120", "page": 589, "page_order": 9, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-07-11", "text": "Awesome game, a childhood memory for me and a classic for any gamer out there.\nBut BUGS, BUGS AND MORE BUGS on the PC version is not so good, after a lot of restarts and downgrades and silent patches, i gave up and uninstalled without finishing it.\nI dont know if i can recommend the PC version to anyone, but this game on consoles i would recommend to everyone. Its unique.", "hours": 6.2, "username": "Tiggazmeister", "products": 245, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
