{"product_id": "12120", "page": 590, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-07-11", "text": "My go to game few years back whenever I was bored. Just open up GTA San Andreas and do whatever you want to do. Complete side missions, drive around listening to in-game radio or just have some crazy fun. Graphical style is really quite different, or even one can say dull compared to other GTA games; even Vice City which is older.\nPros:\n-Good and long story\n-Some interesting characters\n-Lots of side activities..... well it's GTA\n-Huge area to explore and have fun, both city and country side\n-Improvement on gameplay mechanics over previous GTA game\nCons:\n-Graphics seems little dull, even Vice City looks ok years afterwards", "hours": 158.7, "username": "mayu", "products": 74, "early_access": false}
