{"product_id": "12120", "page": 690, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-01-31", "text": "Got this game as a Preorder-Bonus for GTA V and wanted to get back to SA to refresh the awesome moments i had with this game in the past. As it turns out this version on steam just does not work as it should and is sadly a disappointment. I am very happy that i could play this game in its not broken state in the past.\n- Controlls with mouse and keyboard are not what they used to be\n- Songs were removed from the Radio\n- the game crashes all the time on a very powerful PC (the old version (2008) on my \u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665, old netbook still works fine)\nWithout these gamebraking new features this game is one of the best games i have played.... why would you do this to such a cool game", "hours": 0.5, "user_id": "76561198028575315", "username": "TheKoyote", "products": 147, "early_access": false}
