{"product_id": "12120", "page": 694, "page_order": 8, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-01-27", "text": "Somewhere, someone in Rockstar Studios decided to \"update\" their game, nearly ten years after release, to make it ultimately inferior - a worse product. They removed songs, replaced textures, removed details, and generally downgraded it. They decided to take away developers from certain development teams (such as the Grand Theft Auto V development team) to make this version worse.\nThis is absolutely and completely stupid. I beg of you to not purchase this product, and, if you already own it, to write a poor review for it to inform Rockstar Studios of their mistake so that this version may, possibly, be fixed. I want only the best version of Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas to be on Steam. This is truly a fantastic game, though this is a poor version.", "hours": 26.0, "username": "Female Corrin's #1 Fangirl", "products": 133, "found_funny": 4, "early_access": false}
