{"product_id": "12120", "page": 765, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2014-11-07", "text": "The game is great. Been playing it since 2007 (Had the retail copy)... But the last new update completely ruined the game...\nEdit: The update makes V1.0 crash more (Let's face it. 80% of the people play SA-MP/MTA if not more). This is a great example why there should be a downgrade/no updates option on steam. The pirated version/Retail is better (I don't encourage Pirating but if you bought the game, there shouldn't be any guilt)", "hours": 61.4, "username": "TheHolocoaster csgofast.com", "products": 603, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
