{"product_id": "12120", "page": 814, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-06-28", "text": "This game is undoubtedly the best in the GTA series, excluding GTA V. It has that Rockstar sense of humor that we've grown to love. From political satire to pop culture references, this game has it all. This game had a large purple\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665\u2665weapon WELL before Saints Row: The Third. It has numerous mods including graphical enhancement mods that bring the RAGE engine ragdoll physics from GTA IV. This game is a must have for its nostalgic feel, amazing soundtrack, sprawling map, and high modability\n10/10", "hours": 47.3, "user_id": "76561198071910374", "username": "Napolean Born2party", "products": 72, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
