{"product_id": "12120", "page": 853, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-03-24", "text": ",The best Grand Theft Auto from Playstation 2, More better Storyline than other GTA Series,So brilliant games its made me Childhood day ,all love this Game. And Still my Favorite Games,No need to think buy the Original Copies right? its Good Enough. The main Character is Carl Johnson you can Play as other Person to... How? Just Modded it :P\nHas Four Place with Different People,Mysteries, and Things! Over 100+ Missions to do,Spray Tags to get Weapon on Save points,and Extra Missions to get more Playable Fun. Not Fun again? Ya all can play it Multiplayer, Role Playing, DayZ Mods, Aggressive multiplayer! and other fu*king People you can Slay as you want! and Don't forget to Mod it to,to Get more Fun on this Game.\n\"\n\"", "hours": 7.6, "username": "RiivvaaL <3  SBOBETASIA.COM", "products": 332, "early_access": false}
