{"product_id": "12120", "page": 871, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-21", "text": "This game is a work of art. This game is old but i strongly encourage you to play it. But play it with a controller. I played this with the logitech f710 set to direct input. You can map every button exept the pause button, but nevertheless this game is 99% fully controllable .", "hours": 40.4, "user_id": "76561198103811265", "username": "Lizard", "products": 104, "early_access": false}
