{"product_id": "12120", "page": 871, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-21", "text": "Doing my third playthrough on pc now.\nBest GTA ever. Storyline and the sound tracks are great even if it is a 'old' game.\nI also recommend installing multiplayer mod. great Fun! :)\n10/10", "hours": 56.3, "username": "DavisonSR", "products": 117, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 871, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-21", "text": "I would definetly recommend this game! Everyone would go for the newer GTA's but this is the real deal it is soo much fun. Also a tip is to complete the firefighter and ambulance missions first by going into fire truck and ambulance. They are easy and get you fast cash. This game has everything gta 4 has. It is not terribly large game in disk space but its bigger than gta 4 and takes less time to download and its cheaper\n--Spiralin\nP.S Please reply i want to see you reviews", "hours": 187.0, "user_id": "76561198118310888", "username": "Darkridge2000", "products": 31, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 871, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-21", "text": "Pros: Unlike GTA3 and VC, this has proper third person shooter mechanics. Immense customization. Hilarious satire. Well-written characters, dialog(with James Woods, Samuel L. Jackson and David Cross in roles perfect for them) and plot. Great RPG elements, and they're largely optional. Missions are well-designed, memorable and fun. Tense without being unbeatable.\nCons: Graphics are washed out, and when it's dark and in a small enclosed area(tunnel or alley), it can get straining to look at. Camera too often needs manual adjustment. Flying is still tough and it's necessary to complete the game - there is a flight school, but it's too restrictive, linear and you have to go through it before you get to fly much(and once you finally do get past the school, you start actually learning and getting a feel for the planes and helicopters).\nMy recommendation: If you enjoy the GTA series, you have got to play this.", "hours": 48.7, "user_id": "76561198019557045", "username": "A.G.B.", "products": 77, "early_access": false}
