{"product_id": "12120", "page": 871, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-20", "text": "Amazing probably the best GTA game to this date, definitly not the best game graphicly (because it was released in early 2005 :P) but gameplay wise you never run out of things to do, getting 100% completion will by far take you months, and the map is endlessly big with 3 cities (Los Angeles, San Fransisco, and Las Vegas), the woods that are filled with myths and creatures, and a desert complete with Area 51 :). Overall if you are looking for a fun game get this or GTA 5, I give this game a definite 10/10.", "hours": 11.7, "username": "A FAT DONKEY 55", "products": 141, "early_access": false}
