{"product_id": "12120", "page": 872, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2014-02-18", "text": "My personal favorite of the PS2 Grand Theft Autos - an absolutely massive world, tons of things to do throughout the entire environment, a decent story spanning three entire cities, wonderful music....this game has it all. I can't recommend this game enough.\nThe one mark against it that I would give the PC version is that it does not have any 16:9 screen resolutions by default - you'll have to do some modding yourself in order to get it to work in the appropriate resolution which is extremely disappointing. But aside from that minor technical issue, an absolutely wonderful game, and a must-have for any person looking to build their game collection.", "hours": 0.2, "username": "Jragghen", "products": 1162, "early_access": false}
