{"product_id": "12120", "page": 905, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-14", "text": "Hi today i'm reviewing GTA SAN ANDREAS. I enjoy this game deeply, whether you are messing about or following a story. This game is exccelent! I have played 150 hours and counting of this gorgues game. The cartoony look makes this game stand out from the croud, I know the new GTA's such as GTA VI and GTA V are realistic but that takes messing around out of the eqation.\nI just love this game I can only give this game ***** /5 stars PLAY THIS GAME IT'S OUT ON PC FOR THOSE WHO DO NOT HAVE A  PLAYSTAITION 2 AND AVALIBLE ON STEAM!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!", "hours": 175.0, "user_id": "76561198093094235", "username": "smetcalfe8", "products": 21, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 905, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-14", "text": "This game is a definite must have I loved Gta 3 and Vice City but this is taking the GTA series on a whole new level honestly one of the best GTA games I have played. It has things such as respect weapons skills stamina muscle fat strength and sex appeal each one alters gameplay like whenever you get your weapon skill to a high level you can dual wield SMGs and have better accuracy with weapons and things of that sort. It has a great open world and a great story line but if that is not enough for you to buy it right now then also cheats are back but with new and more fun there are also mods from other websites so if youre feeling like just messing around and having a good time then you should for sure get GTA San Andreas I would rate it at 10/10", "hours": 98.4, "username": "\u30c4ZaCHiGa\u2602", "products": 124, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "12120", "page": 905, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-12-12", "text": "An utterly fantastic game. After a couple patches to get the right resolution and fix a rare colour issue, and you have one of the best gaming experiences yet. The driving feels great, gunplay is fun and dynamic, and RPG systems make the game even deeper. CJ's voice actor is spot on, despite being heard the background of a phone call yelling at a NES and having no previous voice acting. CJ is completely customizable, but also requires some maintainence. You have to keep yourself fed and excercized to sprint longer and punch harder, but by the end of the game you are a complete badass.", "hours": 151.4, "username": "Your Gay Father", "products": 482, "early_access": false}
