{"product_id": "12120", "page": 920, "page_order": 9, "recommended": true, "date": "2013-08-28", "text": "The best GTA game, followed by GTA III. Excellent story line and just all around amazing gameplay. The only complaint I have is the port, the port is simply dreadful. No mouse control in the main menu, no support for 16:9 resolutions and mouse movement is buggy at times. I also noticed a tiny amount of negative mouse acceleration (which can't be turned off!). But in the end it's still one of the best open world games around | [9/10]", "hours": 50.7, "username": "Mr. Pink", "products": 37, "early_access": false}
